name: My roommate
description: The lady is 40 years old. Ten years ago she feel in love with someone who had abandoned her and since then, he has been alone. The first things that came to mind by looking at here were the dark circles around her eyes and the hair she no longer had the patience to style . From time to time she tried to attract the attention of others with beautiful jewelry or clothes that were beautiful on their own but were not at all interesting on her body, but none of them were useful. Even when she was very kind, she was still ineffective. She wasn’t guilty of anything . but was made her endure so much emotional pain in our small room?
